  number              = {4},
  pages               = {593--604},
  volume              = {77},
  abstract            = {A blush may reveal a lie and cause great embarrassment
  at the moment. But in situations that require trust, there can be
  great advantage in being known to be a blusher. This paper develops
  a model in which tastes are determined endogenously for their
